:run
Run

Re-executes the contents of the edit buffer.

:edit
PostScript Source

This is an editable text window that contains
the PostScript source of the current document.

:clearoutput
Clear output log

Clears the log of output and errors without 
confirmation.

:output
Output

This is a non-editable text window that shows
the output of the current document, including
error messages.

