:printorfile
Destination:

Determines whether you are printing to a file
or directly to a printer.

Click SELECT on your choice of Printer or File.

:printer
Printer:

Type the name of the printer to send the file to. 

:printdir
Directory:

Type the name of the directory to write the file 
to.

#####################50##########################
:printfile
File:

Type the name of the file.

:thispageonly
This page only:

Indicates that you want to print only the 
current page.

Click SELECT on the box to check it. Click
SELECT again to uncheck it.

:print
Print

Sends the page to the printer or file.

