:pageslider
Goto Page:

Use this window to select the page you want to 
view:

o Type the number of the page you want to view  
  and press Return.

o Drag the slider until the number of the page
  you want to view is displayed.  When you 
  release SELECT, PageView displays the page.

o Click SELECT on a tick mark beneath the 
  slider.

